OL,3,CCarer went on spending spree with
OL,4,Cpensioner's bank cards, court hears
OL,6,FA carer has told Jersey's Royal Court
OL,7,Fshe mistakenly used her "frail"
OL,8,Fclient's credit and debit cards whilst
OL,9,Fshe was rushing to buy Christmas
OL,10,Fpresents for her family.
OL,12,FSandra Natalie Jardim De Sousa is on
OL,13,Ftrial for allegedly stealing thousands
OL,14,Fof pounds from the housebound 80-year-
OL,15,Fold she was entrusted to look after.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
