OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778263866
OL,3,CCarer went on spending spree with
OL,4,Cpensioner's bank cards, court hears
OL,6,FEarlier in the trial, the court heard
OL,7,Fthat between November 2024 and March
OL,8,F2025, 43-year-old Ms De Sousa
OL,9,Fallegedly used her client's card to
OL,10,Fmake large purchases for herself at
OL,11,Fshops around St Helier.
OL,13,FReceipts include one from Boots
OL,14,Fchemist for #266, one from Jersey
OL,15,FTelecom for #344, and another for #146
OL,16,Ffrom department store Voisins.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
