CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778263866
OL,3,CCarer went on spending spree with
OL,4,Cpensioner's bank cards, court hears
OL,6,FThe spending included luxury food
OL,7,Fitems such as serrano ham, chorizo and
OL,8,Fyellowfin tuna, none of which the 80-
OL,9,Fyear-old said she would ever have
OL,10,Fbought.
OL,12,FShe told the court: "I don't even know
OL,13,Fwhat tenderstem broccoli is."
OL,15,FThat was confirmed by her niece and
OL,16,Fother carers who had looked after her.
OL,18,FPC Jess Brown, who investigated the
OL,19,Fcase, said: "I know Marks and
OL,20,FSpencer's is expensive, but that was a
OL,21,Flot of food for one woman."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
