OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778263866
OL,3,CCarer went on spending spree with
OL,4,Cpensioner's bank cards, court hears
OL,6,FDuring cross-examination on Thursday
OL,7,F(7 May), prosecutors challenged Ms De
OL,8,FSousa over what they described as a
OL,9,Fpattern of spending inconsistent with
OL,10,Fthe pensioner's "basic lifestyle".
OL,12,FThe court heard claims that on
OL,13,FChristmas Eve, when Ms De Sousa
OL,14,Fallegedly had just #17.50 in one bank
OL,15,Faccount, the elderly woman's card was
OL,16,Fused for hundreds of pounds worth of
OL,17,Fpurchases.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
