PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778263866
OL,3,CCarer went on spending spree with
OL,4,Cpensioner's bank cards, court hears
OL,6,FProsecutors questioned how she could
OL,7,Fmistakenly use a different coloured
OL,8,Fcard, enter the correct PIN number,
OL,9,Fand still not realise it belonged to
OL,10,Fsomeone else.
OL,12,FMs De Sousa told jurors some purchases
OL,13,Fwere genuine mistakes while she was
OL,14,Frushed and stressed, insisting cash
OL,15,Fwithdrawn from the account was
OL,16,Fauthorised and handed back to the
OL,17,Fwoman.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
