PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778263866
OL,3,CCarer went on spending spree with
OL,4,Cpensioner's bank cards, court hears
OL,6,FMs De Sousa argued the client
OL,7,Ffrequently gave her the card to buy
OL,8,Fgroceries, and to take out cash for
OL,9,Fher when she needed it.
OL,11,FHowever, Lucy McDonald, the resident
OL,12,Fmanager of Aurum Home Care, the
OL,13,Fcompany which employed Ms De Sousa,
OL,14,Fclaimed it was not policy for carers
OL,15,Fto use clients' cards - and that the
OL,16,Ffinancial logs for the client's
OL,17,Faccount are missing.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
