FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778263866
OL,3,CCarer went on spending spree with
OL,4,Cpensioner's bank cards, court hears
OL,6,FThe defence accused the police of
OL,7,Fhaving "tunnel vision", by failing to
OL,8,Fproperly investigate other carers, a
OL,9,Fsecond credit card, and other
OL,10,Ffinancial records.
OL,12,FThe investigating officer rejected
OL,13,Fthat, telling jurors they had explored
OL,14,Fmultiple lines of inquiry.
OL,16,FMs De Sousa has pleaded not guilty to
OL,17,Fall 12 charges: four of larceny and
OL,18,Feight of obtaining goods under false
OL,19,Fpretences.
OL,21,FThe trial continues.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
